{
  "stem": "1550.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we tried to-- we tried to entertain ourselves.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had schools.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had our own football team.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You name it, we got it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had coffee houses.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had theater groups.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had several theater groups.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had a-- we had a music-- we had a music band called The [INAUDIBLE] Boys, The [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was a big scandal at one time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "One of the [INAUDIBLE] Boys got one of the-- got one-- a British girl from high society, got her pregnant.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he had to leave the-- he had to leave the band as a result of that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was a very good looking fellow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they fell in love, and she got pregnant.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was a terrible scandal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Terrible scandal, I'll tell you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he had to leave the band.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- I left Mauritius in March of 1945.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, what happened was that during the war, the Zionist authorities approached or appealed to the British to allow a Jewish division to be formed-- to be formed to fight against the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, the-- the British didn't want to do that for political reasons.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they figured-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Didn't want.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But eventually, Mr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Churchill, I think, was persuaded to-- to-- to agree to that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And eventually, I think in 1944 or so-- I'm not sure about the date-- the Jewish Brigade Group was formed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, there were 30,000 Jews had-- had enlisted from Palestine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were spread over many units, all kinds of small Jewish units.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "A company here, and a-- and a battalion here, but they were all in different formations.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Many were in the Eighth Army that were fighting in North Africa against Rommel.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was all part of the British army.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh yes, yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
